ggplot(dataset, aes(x = school_type, y = n_student)) +
geom_point()

3.creating a line graph.

ggplot(dataset, aes(x = school_type, y = n_student)) +
geom_line()

3.Creating a Bar Graph

ggplot(dataset, aes(x = dataset$school_type, y = dataset$n_student)) +
geom_col()

creating a histogram
